name: Baby Bare wipes
description:
Our minky cloth wipes are super soft and are backed with unbleached bamboo terry towel. These wipes are great for faces, hands, and bottoms. Using these wipes instead of disposable wet wipes is a great way to avoid the chemicals you find in packaged wipes. They're particularly great when your baby has nappy rash as they let you avoid the irritants (like soap and fragrances) found in disposable wipes.

The wipes measure 25cm × 25cm and come in a range of beautiful colours. Choose a pastel or brights pack, or a mix of both.

name: Baby bare Change mats
description:
As a parent, you are constantly changing nappies while out and about. If you worry about putting your baby down on a public change table or bench, or stress about a potentially messy nappy change, you need one of our change mats.

This mat has be specially designed for the family on the go. It folds down into a compact bundle. It's waterproof and beautifully soft for your baby. The mat is made from colourful minky and backed with waterproof PUL. What's even better: it dries super quickly so that it's always ready to go.

The change mats are $11 each. Intro
